README.txt
==========
This module enables multisite Drupal to run cron across all sites or 
a specific set of sites.

INSTALLATION
============
Unarchive into your sites modules directory. Visit admin/settings/multicron
to setup which sites you want to batch cron. Make sure cron is running on
the site you installed the module in.

TROUBLESHOOTING
===============
Is cron running?

